---
lang: ja
layout: _layout/_base.njk
headerType: public
footerType: public
title: お問い合わせ完了
description: お問い合わせありがとうございました。内容を確認のうえ、担当者よりご連絡いたします。
url: https://ohenro.online/ja/contact-us/complete/
---
{% import "_components/_page-title-main.njk" as title %}
{% from "_components/_breadcrumbs.njk" import breadcrumbs %}
{% import "_components/_button-big.njk" as primary %}
<div class="contact-us">
  <div class="page-heading">
		<div class="page-heading__title">
      {{ title.pageTitle("お問い合わせ完了", "", "Complete") }}      
		</div>
		<div class="page-heading__breadcrumbs">
			{{ breadcrumbs([{ label: "お問い合わせ", url: "/contact-us" }, { label: "お問い合わせ完了" }], lang) }}
		</div>
	</div>
  <div class="contact-us__wrapper">
    <section class="contact-us__inner">
      <div class="auth-completion__title">
        {{title.pageTitle("お問い合わせありがとうございます。")}}
        <p class="auth-completion__title-description">後日担当者より改めてご連絡させていただきます。<br />お問い合わせ内容については、確認の上、ご返信させていただきます。</p>
      </div>
      <form class="auth-completion__form">
        <div class="auth-completion__buttons is-single-button">
        {{ primary.primaryButton("トップページ", "link", "/" + lang) }} 
      </div>
      </form>         
    </section>
  </div>
</div>